      "prompt": "已确认场景为 efficiency-label-rate，请基于近 7 天样本池生成只读 QueryPlan，并按机审一级标签、策略 ID、策略名称、送审原因拆分低打标率分级结果。",
      "expected": {
        "trigger": true,
        "scenario_key": "efficiency-label-rate",
        "task_type": "readonly_analysis",
